Having revamped that code, let&#39;s address your question, which apparently is that you want to save the user&#39;s chosen date into another place. I am just guessing at that given (a) your Comments, and (b) I cannot determine the purpose of your second code snippet.

Your `onDateChanged` method reacts to the user choosing a date in the date picker. There you generate your desired text. You store that text in `textView`. You could store it somewhere else too.

```java
